	@echo "⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣧⡀⠛⢈⠄⡀⠀⠀⢡⡻⠓⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡀⠀⠠⡀⢔⣶⣿⣶⠊⢻⠁⠀⣤⣙⢢⠀⠀⠘⢯⡄⠈⠄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠀"
